{"tid":1558958,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惠譽相應調低港鐵評級至AA　展望評級為負面","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:12:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"97b772df8e90fff4170cc3c593eb56429da7c4f0","tid":1558958,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1479893_1_L_20190910231824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1479893_1_L_20190910231824.jpg&h=d6486dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n惠譽繼下調香港評級後，相應調低港鐵長期外幣及本幣發行人違約評級，由AA+下調至AA，前景展望評級為負面。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽指，調低港鐵評級是基於與政府關係緊密，故評級亦會作出相近調整。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽較早前將香港評級下調一級至「AA」，是24年以來首次調低，展望評級為負面。惠譽指，近期香港的衝突及暴力事件，令國際對香港管治制度及法治的看法造成長期損害，香港持續融入國家治理體系，亦帶來更大的監管挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479893-20190910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479893-20190910.htm&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4ajPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=cfb25982\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479893-20190910.htm&h=f38b9ee7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479893-20190910.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bc156c82d1acc60a987e45ce02229ce83a2a1ce6","tid":1558958,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"[超合作運動] 全球齊篤灰 #wtsappforhk #standwithhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拉埋外國勢力齊篤灰</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ecf9ccd34c3364a878e0f08dc416ba286ae3babb","tid":1558958,"uid":88373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"777: 我唔同意"},{"pid":"4e52